IAM Term: 1)Principle 2)Request 3)Authentication 4)Authorized 5)Action/Operation 6)Resources

You can create a new IAM Policy in the Aws management console 3 ways. 1)json :you can create your own json syntax 2)/visual editor : you can constract a new policy from scratch in the visual editor . 3)Import: you can import a managed policy within your aws account.
